1. *Džin* je bio zatvoren u boci hiljadama godina. (The *genie* was trapped in a bottle for thousands of years.)
2. Videla sam *džina* kako se kreće kroz noćno nebo. (I saw a *giant* moving through the night sky.)
3. U bajkama se često pojavljuju *džinovi*. (Fairy tales often feature *genies*.)
4. Njegov *džinovski* apetit ga je činio nepopularnim na večerama. (His *huge* appetite made him unpopular at dinner parties.)
5. *Džinovska* grdosija je stajala pred njima. (A *gigantic* monstrosity stood before them.)
6. Bio je to *džin* od čoveka, visok i snažan. (He was a *giant* of a man, tall and strong.)
7. Na izložbi su prikazani *džinovski* dinosaurusi. (The exhibition featured *gigantic* dinosaurs.)
8. *Džin* je bio ljut zbog toga što ga je neko probudio iz sna. (The *genie* was angry because someone had woken him up from his sleep.)
9. Deca su se igrala sa *džinovskim* balonima. (The children played with *giant* balloons.)
10. Njegov *džinovski* ego ga je sprečavao da prihvati kritiku. (His *enormous* ego prevented him from accepting criticism.)